/img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/12/143829_09264ebb369694a6c1f89c1bab9d90c1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F12%2F143829_09264ebb369694a6c1f89c1bab9d90c1.jpg&h=b15d20c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d84b54136662cacea6fa12793c98d7dd40e2388","tid":355444,"uid":13495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T06:46:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有得佢推囉 唔通唔俾咩又唔係犯法<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/12/143829_09264ebb369694a6c1f89c1bab9d90c1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F12%2F143829_09264ebb369694a6c1f89c1bab9d90c1.jpg&h=b15d20c5&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n整個心心眼俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c03825e29b70867fb1428d1d95b7b73196eb6ebb","tid":355444,"uid":105632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T06:48:22.000Z","msg":"推鳩人已經仆街<br />\n有啲撚樣仲要著撚住盞高燈嚟推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eff6119b1a20aca8a89d9cf11d0296c77a5b7bf","tid":355444,"uid":38898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T07:20:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>假設你係慢線，合法車速行駛，快線一直都無人，但後車係咁推你駛到勁埋</blockquote><br />\n驚乜撚野, 咪由佢推<br />\n<br />\n佢愈推你就應該愈慢tim<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n再推打死火燈 重brake<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n撞左好撚煩，就算有錢收都搵著自己黎攪"},{"pid":"f580cce1ae39d60af2a5646b4341cc5c6d9db0b2","tid":355444,"uid":38898,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T07:22:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你有你均速揸，佢有佢推<br />\n推推下無癮就走架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n揸車啫，心平氣和啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有時俾太太揸車，中/慢線正常限速俾人推我叫佢望前，睇少陣鏡話知佢"},{"pid":"c8917a2b14620931fca6ee20e9ad3c66f75cd99b","tid":355444,"uid":38898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T07:22:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果咁岩想換車呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n撞左就無直版任驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}